Docs.typeparam: The type of the items in the list.
Docs.summary: Represents a chunk list that contains a list of health state chunk items.

remarks.para: The chunk list is obtained from queries that can potentially have more results than can fit a message. Only the entries that fit are returned. The list included the total number of items that should have been returned if there was enough space.
